### List cases (judge + year)
GET http://localhost:8000/cases?judge=maria%20rodriguez&year=2023
Accept: application/json

### List cases (by year only)
GET http://localhost:8000/cases?year=2024
Accept: application/json

### Get case details
GET http://localhost:8000/cases/CASE-000123
Accept: application/json

